        "name": "Magic Reflection",
        "short": "Dealing 1D4 damage",
        "hasResource": false,
        "resource": "",
        "details": "When you take damage from a spell or magical effect, you can use your reaction to magically reflect a spark of that energy back to its source. Dealing 1D4 damage, of the same type that has been inflicted on you, back to your assailant.  \n\nYou can use this benefit a number of times equal to your Proficiency Bonus, per Long Rest. You cannot use this feature if you’re incapacitated.",
        "open": true
      },
      {
        "name": "You Cannot Hide from Me",
        "short": "Faerie Fire / Day",
        "hasResource": false,
        "resource": "",
        "details": "Through your years of training under the Gladius clan, you’ve learnt to reveal what others conceal by learning the secrets of Faerie Fire*. You’re able to cast it once per long rest without the use of a spell slot. You can also cast Faerie Fire with any spell slots that you have. \n",
        "open": true
